list.name: Default
list.comment: Completely refactored Router, added SubRouter as well as a subrouting system (modular via traits and abstract classes)

task.summary: Refactored several parts, cleaned up code, updated from PHP7.0.1 to PHP7.1.11
Modified tests (update from mods), refactored tiny pieces of code
Modified scripts (CRLF => LF) to work on any platform/shell variant.

Added a dependency (myclabs/php-enum), refactored MagicalArray, added Enum and TypedEnum (and related), refactored HttpRedirectType former HttpRedirectStatus), added ArrayHelper and NamespaceResolver refactored Router, refactored tests, added tests, cleaned up code
Refactored the Router class to minimize what it is really doing (separation of concerns), separated Router in several classes/interfaces/traits to be able to reuse the same code for future SubRouter
Completely refactored Router, added SubRouter as well as a subrouting system (modular via traits and abstract classes)
